4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior knowledge in the field. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online sessions per week, accommodating up to 18 participants per class. Students will acquire foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced techniques in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Training covers risk management and compliance with international standards, such as ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop